Description:
Sophisticated hotel rooms, suites & apartments, plus a restaurant, a lounge bar & a rooftop pool.
Set in the city centre, this cosmopolitan hotel is a minute's walk from Her Majesty's Theatre, a 2-minute walk from Chinatown and a 6-minute walk from Parliament train station.
The airy, contemporary rooms offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, and tea and coffeemaking facilities. Some feature living areas, and room service is available 24/7. Suites add dining spaces; some have marble bathrooms, whirlpool baths and additional bedrooms. Apartments add kitchenettes.
An elegant restaurant features a sleek lounge bar. A heated rooftop pool and an exercise room are available, as well as a business centre, 10 meeting rooms and parking (fee).

Name: ibis Melbourne - Hotel & Apartments
Description:
Laid-back hotel with functional rooms & apartments with kitchenettes, plus a restaurant & a bar.
This funky high-rise hotel is 0.6 km from Queen Victoria Market, 1.3 km from Flinders Street train station and 1.5 km from the Melbourne Museum.
The modern, streamlined rooms provide Wi-Fi (fee), flat-screen TVs and iPod docks, plus minifridges, and tea and coffeemaking facilities. Polished 1- and 2-bedroom apartments add kitchenettes and lounge areas.
An airy, modern eatery offers casual fare and a breakfast buffet. Other amenities include a bar with a pool table, a business centre, and 3 meeting rooms. Parking is available for a fee.

Name: Glenferrie Hotel
Description:
Cosy Victorian restaurant and bar, plus straightforward rooms with whirlpool baths and free Wi-Fi.
A 4-minute walk from the Glenferrie train station, this enduring hotel with a stately facade and a Victorian pub is 8 km from both Federation Square and the Royal Botanic Gardens.
The subdued rooms feature free Wi-Fi, 107-cm flat-screens, and tea and coffeemaking facilities, plus whirlpool baths. Room service is available.
Amenities include a cosy restaurant and a Victorian bar with vintage details, in addition to an elegant lobby with leather seating and a grandfather clock. Parking is complimentary.

Name: Sunshine Motor Inn
Description:
Straightforward motel featuring an outdoor pool & a restaurant/bar, as well as free parking & Wi-Fi.
This unfussy motel is 10 km from walking trails in Brimbank Park, 8 km from Maribyrnong River Trail and a 12-minute walk from More Park.
Humble rooms and suites offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, and tea and coffeemaking facilities, as well as minifridges. Some have sitting areas and/or whirlpool baths.
Parking is complimentary. Other amenities include a restaurant/bar, an outdoor pool and a meeting room, plus a hot tub. Breakfast is available.
Categories: Motel, Bar & grill, Family restaurant, Function room facility, Meeting room

Name: Hotel 115 / 115 Grill & Brewhouse
Description:
Upmarket hotel with free Wi-Fi & stylish rooms, plus a grill restaurant & brewery.
This upscale hotel is 9.1 km from the National Gallery of Victoria and 10.1 km from the Royal Botanic Gardens.
All of the stylish, warm rooms have Wi-Fi and offer 42-inch flat-screen TVs, Apple iMac minis and desks, as well as minifridges and coffeemakers. Some add private balconies, whirlpool tubs, full kitchens with microwaves, and sofabeds.
There’s a contemporary grill restaurant and brewery, plus fitness facilities and meeting spaces. Other amenities include coin-operated laundry facilities and parking.

Name: Plum Serviced Apartments.
Description:
Down-to-earth suites & apartments in a straightforward hotel offering a terrace with BBQs.
A 10-minute walk from Central Melbourne train station, this simple all-suite hotel lies 11 minutes on foot from the enduring Queen Victoria Market and 3 km from the National Gallery of Victoria.
The down-to-earth suites have free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and DVD players, as well as tea and coffeemaking equipment. All provide living areas, while studios and 1-bedroom apartments add kitchenettes and dishwashers.
Amenities include a guest lounge with a flat-screen TV and a DVD player, plus a courtyard terrace with BBQ facilities. Coin-operated laundry facilities are on-site, and parking is available.

Name: Zagame's House
Description:
Chic rooms & suites in a trendy hotel offering a restaurant/cafe, a wine bar & a gym.
In the Central Business District, this trendy hotel is a 14-minute walk from Queen Victoria Market, 8 minutes away on foot from the Melbourne Museum and a 4-minute walk from the nearest tram stop.
Chic rooms feature flat-screen TVs, Wi-Fi and safes, in addition to minifridges and coffeemakers. Upgraded rooms add wet bars. Suites offer separate living areas. There's also room service.
Amenities include a cool restaurant/cafe, a wine bar and a gym. Breakfast and parking are available.

Name: The Prince Hotel
Description:
Laid-back property featuring a Mediterranean restaurant & a bar, as well as free Wi-Fi.
A 7-minute walk from St. Kilda Beach, this laid-back hotel is 1 km from amusement rides at Luna Park Melbourne and 6 km from Royal Botanic Gardens Victoria.
The casual, airy rooms feature free Wi-Fi, flat-screens and safes, plus minibars and tea and coffeemaking facilities. Upgraded rooms add balconies. Suites feature separate living areas.
There's a trendy Mediterranean restaurant and a bar with regular live music. Breakfast is available for a fee.

Name: The Cullen Melbourne - Art Series
Description:
Hip, artist-inspired boutique hotel offering a casual bistro, a dumpling bar & a gym.
A 1-minute walk from a tram stop, this hip boutique hotel featuring artwork by artist Adam Cullen is 4 km from the National Gallery of Victoria and 6 km from Federation Square.
The modern studio suites, which feature original artwork and designer furniture, have free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, plus kitchenettes with minifridges and microwaves. Upgraded suites add balconies and/or separate living areas. Room service is available.
Amenities include a laid-back bistro and a dumpling bar, as well as an exercise room, a business centre and conference rooms. Parking and breakfast are available for a fee.

Name: United Places Hotel Botanic Gardens
Description:
Streamlined suites with kitchens in an ultrahip boutique hotel with fine dining & butler service.
In a contemporary concrete-and-glass building featuring specially commissioned artwork, this ultrahip boutique hotel is opposite the Royal Botanic Gardens and 2 km from Flinders Street train station.
With designer furniture and bespoke fabrics, the streamlined 1- and 2-bedroom suites come with kitchens, living rooms and balconies. All have free Wi-Fi, smart TVs, washing machines and minibars; some offer garden views. Complimentary breakfast is served in-room. Butler service is available.
There's a high-end, rustic-chic restaurant.

Name: Next Hotel Melbourne, Curio Collection by Hilton
Description:
Chic quarters in a trendy, high-end hotel featuring a cafe, a restaurant & a bar, plus a gym.
Set among shops and bars, this hip, high-end hotel is 18 minutes' walk from the National Gallery of Victoria, 6 km from Port Melbourne Beach and 22 km from Melbourne Airport.
Featuring original artwork, chic rooms with a contemporary vibe include Wi-Fi, smart TVs and espresso machines. All have minifridges and in-room cocktails; suites provide separate living rooms. Club quarters allow access to a private lounge with evening socials. Room service is available 24/7.
Amenities consist of an upscale bar/restaurant, a trendy cafe and a bar, plus a fitness room and parking.
Fulladdress: Floor 3/103 Little Collins St, Melbourne VIC 3000
Owner: Next Hotel Melbourne, Curio Collection by Hilton (owner)

Name: Carlton Hotel
Description:
Informal rooms in a modern property with a bright restaurant/bar, an outdoor pool & a sauna.
This colourful, contemporary hotel is a 3-minute walk from Ievers Street tram stop, 11 minutes' walk from the Melbourne Zoo and 3 km from the food stalls of Queen Victoria Market.
Relaxed rooms come with complimentary Wi-Fi, as well as flat-screen TVs, minibars, and tea and coffeemaking facilities. Some offer balconies and/or pool views. Kids age 11 and under stay at no extra cost with an adult.
There's an airy restaurant/bar and an outdoor pool. Other amenities include a fitness room, a sauna, a coin-operated laundry and a BBQ area. Breakfast and parking are available (fee).

Name: The Crown Promenade Melbourne
Description:
Contemporary property with an upscale restaurant, plus a pool, a gym & meeting space.
This upscale hotel in the city centre lies 1 km from the National Gallery of Victoria and 2 km from Queen Victoria Market.
The sleek rooms and suites provide free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minifridges, as well as tea and coffeemaking equipment. Suites add sitting areas and dining areas.
There's an international buffet restaurant. Other amenities include an airy indoor pool and a gym, as well as a business centre and meeting space.
Categories: Hotel, Bar, Business to business service, Conference center

Name: Ashley Hotel
Description:
Streamlined rooms in an unpretentious hotel offering an airy sports bar/restaurant, plus free Wi-FI.
Set along Route 8, this unpretentious hotel is 4 km from the 15-hectare Footscray Park along the Maribyrnong River. It's also 8 km from Flemington Racecourse, home of the Melbourne Cup.
The streamlined rooms offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, and tea and coffeemaking facilities, plus minifridges and shared bathrooms. Upgraded rooms add en suite facilities; some sleep up to 3 people.
Parking is complimentary. There's also an airy sports bar/restaurant with a pool table.

Name: The Como Melbourne
Description:
Stylish property featuring a rooftop indoor pool, a cocktail bar & 2 restaurants, plus a sundeck.
Among the upscale shops of South Yarra's Chapel Street, this chic hotel is a 5-minute walk from South Yarra train station and 4 km from the National Gallery of Victoria.
Contemporary rooms offer Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, safes and minibars, as well as tea and coffeemaking facilities; some have whirlpool baths. Suites add living rooms; some feature balconies, or kitchenettes and saunas. Room service is available 24/7.
Amenities include 2 restaurants and a cocktail bar. There's also a sauna, an indoor rooftop pool and a fitness centre, plus a sundeck. Breakfast and parking are offered for a surcharge.

Name: Dorsett Melbourne
Categories: Hotel, Extended stay hotel, Serviced accommodation, Wellness hotel

Name: Holiday Inn Express Melbourne Southbank, an IHG Hotel
Description:
Low-key rooms in a straightforward hotel offering a relaxed restaurant, a bar & a fitness centre.
Facing a busy thoroughfare lined with office buildings and casual eateries, this down-to-earth hotel is a 6-minute walk from the National Gallery of Victoria and 13 minutes on foot from SEA LIFE Melbourne Aquarium. Melbourne Airport is 26 km away.
Streamlined rooms feature Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, as well as minifridges, safes, and tea and coffeemaking equipment. All have en suite, shower-only bathrooms.
A breakfast buffet is served in a relaxed restaurant offering a bar and terrace seating. Other amenities include a fitness centre and coin-operated laundry facilities. Parking is available.
Owner: Holiday Inn Express Melbourne Southbank, an IHG Hotel (owner)

Name: Quest Prahran
Description:
Informal apartment hotel with 1- to 3-bedroom units offering kitchens, living areas & free Wi-Fi.
Set 1 minutes' walk from the nearest tram stop, this relaxed apartment hotel is 4 km from Luna Park, 5 km from the Crown Casino and Entertainment Complex, and 6 km from the Melbourne Central Business District.
The laid-back 1- to 3-bedroom apartments offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and kitchens, plus washer/dryers, and separate living/dining areas. Some units add furnished balconies and/or extra bathrooms.
Parking is available for a fee. Other amenities include meeting rooms.
Categories: Hotel, Extended stay hotel, Serviced accommodation

Name: Roamer St Kilda
Description:
Trendy hostel featuring a restaurant & a communal kitchen, plus a screening room.
Set within a 19th-century building, this trendy hostel is a 16-minute walk from the Luna Park amusement park, 2 km from Windsor train station and 4 km from the Royal Botanic Gardens Victoria.
Understated dorms and private rooms have shared bathrooms. Linens are included. Dorms feature bunk beds and lockers, while upgraded rooms provide en suite facilities and/or sitting areas.
Amenities consist of a restaurant, a communal kitchen and a screening room. Yoga lessons and breakfast are available, as is Wi-Fi.
